dashboard.title: Dashboard & Reports
dashboard.totalCaseTip: Total number of cases received during selected duration for my tenant.
dashboard.successTip: Total number of cases successfully processed to Safety DB during selected duration for my tenant.
dashboard.failureTip: Total number of cases failed to be processed during selected duration for my tenant.
dashboard.processingTip: Total number of cases successfully read, currently under processing for selected duration and tenant.
dashboard.activeTip: Total no. of users who have logged in to the portal at least once during selected period.
dashboard.inactiveTip: Total no. of users who have not logged in to the portal even once during selected period.
dashboard.unassignedTip: Total number of cases which are currently unassigned to any tenant and require immediate action.
dashboard.totalCaseClientTip: Total number of cases received during selected duration for selected tenants.
dashboard.successClientTip: Total number of cases successfully processed to Safety DB during selected duration for selected tenants.
dashboard.failureClientTip: Total number of cases failed to be processed during selected duration for selected tenants.
dashboard.note: NOTE: This chart shows data for Top 10 tenants of the client. If there is no case processed for any tenant, that tenant will not be shown on the chart.
